Package application

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    InfoScreenController
    Defines the controller for the StartScreen.FXML document
    Main
    Defines the Main for starting the JavaFX application.
    MainTest
    To test JavaFX you need to ensure that it is initialised first, once initialised you can not initialise it multiple times so must do so only once for all tests.
    MyStage
    Defines the main logic for the program and contains all the graphics.
    ScoreBoardModelTest
    Unit tests for the ScoreBoard Model.
    ScoreTest
    Unit testing for the Score Class
    StartScreenController
    Defines the controller for the StartScreen.FXML document
    World
    Defines the logic for the Pane in the program, this predominantly sets the event handlers and manages interactions between nodes on the pane it self.
